        "summary": "Avalo Therapeutics reported its first quarter 2026 financial results and provided recent business updates. The most significant news is the positive topline results from the Phase 2 LOTUS trial of abdakibart (AVTX-009) in patients with moderate to severe hidradenitis suppurativa (HS). The trial met its primary endpoint, with abdakibart showing a statistically significant absolute improvement in HiSCR75 response rates compared to placebo at Week 16. Avalo plans to advance abdakibart into a registrational Phase 3 program. The company also highlighted a major public offering completed on May 7, 2026, which raised $431.3 million in gross proceeds.",
