        "summary": "AnaptysBio announced its first quarter 2026 financial results and provided an update on its transitioned business model. Following the spin-off of its biopharma operations into First Tracks Biotherapeutics on April 20, 2026, AnaptysBio now focuses on managing financial collaborations, primarily the royalties for Jemperli (with GSK) and imsidolimab (with Vanda). Jemperli royalties for Q1 2026 reached $313 million, and the company expects significant growth through 2029. Imsidolimab has an upcoming PDUFA date of December 12, 2026, for GPP.",
