        "summary": "Incyte announced that more than 20 abstracts from its Hematology and Oncology pipeline have been accepted for presentation at the EHA 2026 Congress. A key highlight is the Phase 3 frontMIND trial data for tafasitamab in first-line DLBCL, which will be featured in a Plenary Session. The congress will also feature data for INCA033989 in myeloproliferative neoplasms and updates on several other oncology programs including axatilimab. Mentions of collaborations or products related to UCB and Xencor (XNCR) are included in the context of pipeline development or comparative highlights.",
